\id 1TH - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014) 
\h 1 Tes 
\toc3 1 Tes 
\toc1 Polote Dopo Leta Tesalonaika Sose Tawakalubaęž‰tamo Ododiyaęž‰ 
\toc2 1 Tesalonaika 
\mt2 POLOTE DOPO LETA  
\mt1 TESALONAIKA SOSE TAWAKALUBAęž‰TAMO  
\mt2 ODODIYAęž‰  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Na Polote Sailasiko baęž‰gala Timotiko, ale laęž‰ Tesalonaika sose tawakalubaęž‰tamo baęž‰moe leta bepoememaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te Nabiwi Godoko baęž‰gala Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwalo bemedenamata. Wadiyala Godokono malemale komo baęž‰gala ebeno hete komote laęž‰godolo naęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰.   
\s1 Tesalonaika Sose Tawakalubino Hibimaęž‰ Midi Komo  
\p
\v 2 Ale hiliyonomo tetelo laęž‰ hiliyonomoeno komomaęž‰ Godotamo kalakala tabo ba adipate laęž‰ toetoe tabamo baęž‰bo wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelenakata.  
\v 3 Iyo, laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kebe hido komokomo dododilinakuima, baęž‰gala malemale emalagidolo ipuwalo kebe oko helonomamo dowatinamima, baęž‰gala baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰le kodakodalo ba laęž‰motaęž‰hana Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono pe komomaęž‰ daęž‰latiminama, ale Nabiwi Godokono holoholo hapulu baęž‰moi komokomo kadodolenahaęž‰.   
\p
\v 4 Aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, a iyaęž‰tawahala Godote yaęž‰lo tetelo laęž‰ malemalelo ba emalagidolena laęž‰ baęž‰bo uwatiyaęž‰ta laęž‰le ebeno tawakalubimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰.  
\v 5 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ale Yaęž‰sukunu Hido Tabo laęž‰tamo dadahimaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo baęž‰be tabote hopo habanapino mulu tabo gaęž‰la ipuwalo kitanuihaęž‰. Ao, baęž‰be tabote huiyatiya Godokono Gobogoboeno heloamo laęž‰tamo pi, baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰le laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo iyaęž‰tawahuimata baęž‰be tabote Godogodone hibinomolo puluhuku.  
\p Numaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo laęž‰ kowalubilimaęž‰ komo hegelalo laęž‰ ipuwalo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰pemedimaęž‰, baęž‰be komo laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala.  
\v 6 Baęž‰bene Godokono Gobogobogodone duluhukuna, laęž‰le baęž‰be kalakalago ebeno Hido Tabo daęž‰lawima, baęž‰ba tetene tupuimiti hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te koko temeteme laęž‰tamo ba ikalame, laęž‰ huiyatiya aeno emede komomaęž‰ baęž‰gala Kodawa Kelisokono emede komomaęž‰ a baęž‰bo ibamiaęž‰tenapimata.  
\v 7 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰eno ododili komate baęž‰ atumu Maęž‰sadoniya baęž‰gala Guliki hoponapaęž‰tamo gomaęž‰ edaęž‰huyaęž‰, laęž‰le keba kaęž‰na kemedeonama ibaęž‰te ibino hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na naęž‰kemedenamenaęž‰.  
\v 8 Huiyatiya Kodawoeno tabote laęž‰eno ododili ipuwado Maęž‰sadoniya baęž‰gala Guliki hoponapi ibi kapiyatamo katohaęž‰, iyo, baęž‰be tabote geboleno diyamo keba kaęž‰nalaęž‰kaęž‰ hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ muhulu hopamo baęž‰ba kaęž‰na aęž‰tui, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale baęž‰bi hoponapaęž‰tamo daęž‰nikulimaęž‰, ale tabo olamagimihino ibaęž‰te laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komo yaęž‰lo ulihuyaęž‰.  
\v 9 Numaęž‰laęž‰, ibi hiliyonomate naęž‰gaęž‰lana, ale Hido Tabo laęž‰tamo dadahimaęž‰ laęž‰le a kalakalago keba kaęž‰na kuwatiuima, baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te naęž‰kagaęž‰lana, laęž‰le haęž‰da amiho gobogoboeno idaęž‰daęž‰li adikulame ipuwane Kaęž‰kaęž‰dawa baęž‰gala Hibidawa Godoko adikumi komamo keba kaęž‰na kohobilaęž‰huima,  
\v 10 baęž‰gala Godokono Guduti Hunu Habane pemaęž‰ laęž‰le baęž‰be komo daęž‰latiminama, ibaęž‰te baęž‰be komomaęž‰ atumu naęž‰kagaęž‰lana.  
\p Baęž‰moe komo baęž‰ hibila, Godote ebeno Gudu hoe ipuwane kaęž‰kaęž‰mo adipatiyaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰moe Yaęž‰suti a hibimaęž‰ midipino kaęž‰kaęž‰ naęž‰mulaęž‰leaęž‰mena, Godogodone daęž‰pemene baęž‰be konomo mauba komote a puwatekapomaęž‰.   
\c 2  
\s1 Polote Tesalonaika Ko Habalo Godokono Oko Keba Kaęž‰na Kowatinami  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahanomola ale laęž‰ ipuwalo oko owatimaęž‰ daęž‰pelamimaęž‰ baęž‰be oko ipuwalo hidohido gaote ikuliyaęž‰.  
\v 2 Baęž‰gala laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala, ale laęž‰tamo pelameheno dopamo Pilipai habalo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te a iduduputiaęž‰melo temeteme atamo keba kaęž‰na kikaaęž‰mi, baęž‰bene ale laęž‰eno habamo daęž‰pelamimaęž‰ baęž‰bolo komo hiliyonomate atumu a konomamo duhiaęž‰memaęž‰ ba ewagele, huiyatiya aeno Godote tole komo tamaęž‰mo ihateaęž‰mete, ale ebegodone daęž‰pena baęž‰be Hido Tabo laęž‰tamo hidonomamo baęž‰bo polamagimimaęž‰.   
\p
\v 3 Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰le baęž‰moe Hido Tabo hibimaęž‰ komidimaęž‰ ale laęž‰ daęž‰kiyalami, baęž‰ba tetelo ale hibo gabo ududi komodo baęž‰gala tepo ipuwoeno kekaęž‰kekaęž‰ ukui komodo haęž‰da amiho tabo komokomo kagaęž‰lahaęž‰.  
\v 4 Ao, aeno komo eba kaęž‰nahaęž‰, ale huiyatiya tawakalubaęž‰tamo Godokono hibi tabo kapiya bolamagiminakomaęž‰, mabu Godote a ebeno hidohido okopimaęž‰ kaęž‰milo ebeno Hido Tabo olamagimi oko atamo ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰be oko owati ipuwalo aeno ukui baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kitanahaęž‰, ale tawakalubi ba kalakaluilame ibaęž‰te a kawagaminoenamaęž‰, a huiyatiya aeno ubi nihatenakomaęž‰ Godoko kapiya kokalakaluiminamaęž‰, mabu ebete aeno tepo ipuwoeno komokomo hiliyonomo ba ulame baęž‰bo anagilameleaęž‰menako.  
\v 5 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala, a laęž‰go ba pemede ale hunu gabodo laęž‰ awagaminalelo laęž‰tamo nolata tabo kolamagiminakuihaęž‰ komo ilina baęž‰gala mani laęž‰godone kuwatemaęž‰, iyo, Godote aeno hibi komo atumu iyaęž‰tawala aeno tepo ipuwoeno ukuilo baęž‰bako haęž‰da amiho komote laęž‰tamo kitanatihaęž‰!  
\v 6-7 Numaęž‰laęž‰, ale Kelisokono oelamepimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hanamaęž‰ baęž‰be komo koamo emalagidoloheno ale laęž‰ kakiyalamenakuihaęž‰ komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ ilina baęž‰gala mani atamo dito kikaaęž‰mehoemaęž‰, iyo, aeno oko owati ipuwalo ale tawakalubino awagaha komo laęž‰godolo baęž‰gala komopaęž‰godolo kohowadinakuihaęž‰, huiyatiya ale laęž‰ hidamo anukulamenapiaęž‰ta, menokote ebeno gugudi hidamo danukulamenanako baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.   
\p
\v 8-9 O aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰ konomamo nemalagidolenata, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ale Godogodone daęž‰pena baęž‰be Hido Tabo laęž‰tamo ba ikalame laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ aeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ tamaęž‰mo baęž‰bo miyaęž‰tenakuimaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, aeno malemale laęž‰tamo dehaęž‰potomaęž‰ kedaęž‰namihaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale laęž‰ ipuwalo menemene oko ba owati kebe kodakoda komokomo dulamenakuimaęž‰, na iyaęž‰tawala laęž‰ baęž‰bi komo kadodolenahaęž‰. Iyo, du baęž‰gala hegela ale aeno kokotamo oko owatihonakuimaęž‰ a haęž‰kiya aeno modobohaęž‰ komokomo kulamemaęž‰, mabu ale Godokono Hido Tabo olamagimi oko laęž‰godolo ba powati ale eta dehaęž‰poto temeteme laęž‰tamo kikalamemaęž‰ ubihaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰hanakuimaęž‰.   
\p
\v 10 Baęž‰ hibila, ale baęž‰ba tetelo laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi ipuwalo kebe komokomo kododilinakuimaęž‰ baęž‰bi komo baęž‰ tuputupu hibinomola, eta kuba ododi komo kapiyate agodolo kitananakuihaęž‰. Iyo, laęž‰ baęž‰gala Godoko laęž‰le aeno hido-talona emede komo iyaęž‰tawahanomola,  
\v 11 baęž‰gala laęž‰ baęž‰moe eta komo iyaęž‰tawahala, nabaęž‰te ibino gugudi keba kaęž‰na kowalubilinaka, ale laęž‰ hiliyonomo baęž‰ba kaęž‰na owalubilinakuyaęž‰ta.  
\v 12 Numaęž‰laęž‰, komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tetelo ale laęž‰ hido tabo komamo ba owalubili laęž‰ aęž‰kiyalamenakuyaęž‰ta laęž‰le laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo Godokono hidohido gaęž‰limapi gugudimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰, mabu baęž‰be Kodawate laęž‰ kaęž‰lami kekelamenahaęž‰ laęž‰le ebeno Ko Gawadubu Haboeno konomo aęž‰laęž‰mina komo ebaęž‰go kapimilo kolawemaęž‰.  
\v 13 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala ale hiliyonomo tetelo Godotamo kalakala tabo baęž‰gaęž‰lanamaęž‰, mabu Godogodone daęž‰pena laęž‰le baęž‰be tabo agodone dulihuima, baęž‰ba tetelo laęž‰le hopo lumagino tabomaęž‰ kagaęž‰lahaęž‰, huiyatiya laęž‰le kodakodalo lawete Godokono hibi tabonomomaęž‰ midimata. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰be tabo baęž‰ Godokonola, baęž‰bemaęž‰ kebe lumagiti ebe hibimaęž‰ daęž‰midina, baęž‰be tabote ebe ipuwalo hido oko bowatinamene.   
\s1 Yaęž‰suku Mabumaęž‰ Temeteme Komate Tesalonaika Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰tamo Dikulihuyaęž‰  
\p
\v 14 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, Godokono tabote laęž‰ ipuwalo oko dowatina, a baęž‰be komo iyaęž‰tawahala mabu ebeno sose tawakalubaęž‰te Yudiya hopoeno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ habahabalo demedehona, baęž‰bi hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo kebe temeteme komate kikulihuyaęž‰ baęž‰bi atu komate laęž‰tamo aęž‰kikulihuyaęž‰. Iyo, laęž‰eno hoponapaęž‰te laęž‰tamo kebako temeteme kikalameti, dopamo tetelo Yunapino hopolo komopaęž‰te Yaęž‰su Kelisokono taęž‰matapaęž‰tamo baęž‰bako atu temeteme beka-ikalamiyaęž‰.  
\v 15 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰bi hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰ Yunapino komo nemalagidolalaęž‰, Godokono mauba komote ibaęž‰tamo konomamo itana, mabu ibaęž‰te tawakalubi biduhilamena ebetamo pelamemaęž‰! Iyo, ibaęž‰te dopamo Godokono ukui hawakalimipi danakapulamenakui, baęž‰bene baęž‰be atu gabodo Kodawa Yaęž‰suku akanakapumiyaęž‰ baęž‰gala a ebe hibimaęž‰ midipi aeno hopone heloamo dito taęž‰maaęž‰tiyaęž‰.  
\v 16 Baęž‰bene ale aeno hopo miyaęž‰pate muhulu hopolo demedehona baęž‰bi Yuhaęž‰paęž‰tamo tolamete Godokono kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ tabo ibaęž‰tamo olamagimi ba netupuimi, huiyatiya baęž‰bolo komo Yunapaęž‰te a duhiaęž‰memaęž‰ atumu kewageliyaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te baęž‰moe kuititi tetelo baęž‰moe eta konomo kuba ba ododi Godokono holoholo hapulu ibino kuba ododili komate aęž‰tabotabohui, baęž‰moe mabumaęž‰ ebeno konomo mauba komote ibaęž‰tamo baęž‰ aęž‰puluhuku!   
\s1 Polote Tesalonaika Sose Tawakalubaęž‰tamo Gala Tomaęž‰ Ubi Daęž‰kihatiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 17-18 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰ daęž‰miyaęž‰pali baęž‰ba tetene tupuimiti baęž‰ma tetaęž‰mo puluhuku, ale tete nanekelelo aeno katene apaęž‰mo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ ba emedaęž‰tepa huiyatiya aeno tepo ipuwoeno ukuilo ale laęž‰go kapiyanomomaęž‰ edaęž‰hanatimaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ komo hiliyonomo tetelo ale ubi konomamo ihatenakuimaęž‰ laęž‰tamo kapimilo pelamete laęž‰eno holoholo gala kakapulamemaęž‰, baęž‰gala komo tetelo na Poloko na haęž‰kiya pemaęž‰ ewagelenakuimo huiyatiya Saitanate a naęž‰duhiaęž‰menakui.   
\p
\v 19 Baęž‰ hibila, aeno ubi laęž‰tamo konomamo bitana. Numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰ aeno kalakala komoeno mabulata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale Yaęž‰sukunu pe komo naęž‰latiminamaęž‰ mabu ale laęž‰ ebeno holoholo hapulu gala daęž‰kulamemenaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo aeno kalakalate konomomaęž‰ kakedaęž‰maęž‰ne. Iyo, ale Saitanatamo alaholoho ipuwalo daęž‰lawimaęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰ baęž‰be wato kikipolata,  
\v 20 mabu ale Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwalo ba emedena, laęž‰ baęž‰ aeno awagaha komolata baęž‰gala aeno kalakala mabulata.   
\c 3  
\s1 Polote Tesalonaika Sose Tawakalubi Konowalubilimaęž‰ Timotiko Daęž‰noemiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Numaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰tamo kapimilo pelamemaęž‰ gabo nipo dohowadimaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno tepo ipuwalo ukui bilibilimaęž‰ ba edaęž‰ha ale naęž‰gaęž‰luimaęž‰, â€śWadiyala a komopaęž‰te baęž‰moe Aęž‰tenese habalo ba emede,  
\v 2 a ipuwalo aeno hibimaęž‰ mididawa ekawi Timotiko kapiya konoememaęž‰nemaęž‰.â€ť Baęž‰ hibila, ale Yaęž‰sukunu Hido Tabo dolamagiminakomaęž‰ Timotiti ago kapimilo Godokono hido oko bowatina, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale ebe laęž‰tamo aęž‰poemimaęž‰ ebete laęž‰ ba powalubili laęž‰le hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kodakodalo kolaęž‰motaęž‰hanamaęž‰,  
\v 3 mabu a ubihinola hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰pino temeteme ikalame komodo laęž‰ ipuwalo eta kapiyate kubamo alega. Laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahanomola baęž‰mako temetemaęž‰te baęž‰ Godokono ubilo a hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo pikulinaka,  
\v 4 mabu a laęž‰go ba pemede ale laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na aęž‰kiyalamiaęž‰ta, â€śHibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰godone temeteme komate atamo kopikulimaęž‰naęž‰.â€ť Iyo, hibila, baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahanomola baęž‰be komote baęž‰ laęž‰tamo uluhukui.  
\v 5 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, nale baęž‰moe komo ba emalagidolo Timotiko baęž‰bemaęž‰ poemimo, iyo, laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ nale naeno tepo ipuwalo ukui bilibilimaęž‰ ba edaęž‰ ubi baęž‰bo ihatimo, ebete laęž‰go ba pemede laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komokomo hidamo kopulamelelamemaęž‰. Baęž‰ba tetelo na ubihinola laęž‰ komopaęž‰te Saitanakono kuba emogabuimi gabamo daęž‰gudima ebete baęž‰be komo pumi, mabu baęž‰mako komote laęž‰tamo nuluhukutale, ale kebe kodakoda oko laęž‰ ipuwalo dowatimaęž‰ baęž‰be okote dito baęž‰kubanaęž‰!   
\p
\v 6 Huiyatiya Timotiti laęž‰godone atamo gala daęž‰kapi, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ hidonomo tabo atamo adahi, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komote Godotamo kodakodalo itana baęž‰gala laęž‰eno malemale komopaęž‰tamo atumu baęž‰ka-itana, baęž‰gala ebete a naęž‰pekiyaaęž‰mi laęž‰ hiliyonomo tetelo a malemalelo keba kaęž‰na kemalagidoloeonama, iyo, ale laęž‰ ulamemaęž‰ ubi konomamo dihatenamaęž‰ laęž‰ baęž‰ atumu a uaęž‰memaęž‰ ubi naęž‰kihatenamata.  
\v 7 O aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, Timotiti laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komomaęž‰ a daęž‰pikiyaaęž‰mi baęž‰be tabote a hibinomolo aęž‰kalakaluiaęž‰mi! Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ale aeno menemene komo baęž‰gala hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ temeteme komokomo koamo aęž‰kemalagidolaęž‰maęž‰,  
\v 8 mabu keba tetelo laęž‰ Kodawa Yaęž‰suku ipuwalo kodakodalo daęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanama, ale baęž‰be komo dulimaęž‰ baęž‰ba tetelo a ko kalakala lawete aeno emede ipuwalo eta ukui bilibili komote hibilo aęž‰kitanamene.  
\v 9 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale Godokono holoholo hapulu daęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanamaęž‰ laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ aeno kalakala bada konomolaęž‰kaęž‰! Iyo, ale aeno kalakala tabo ebetamo ba wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latele,  
\v 10 hegela baęž‰gala du hiliyonomolo ebe naęž‰toemehonakomaęž‰ ebete a gabo diyaęž‰tuaęž‰memene, ale pelamete laęž‰eno holoholo ba pulame kebe modobohaęž‰ komate laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo daęž‰polaęž‰na baęž‰bi komokomo kopetuputupuilamemaęž‰nemaęž‰.   
\p
\v 11 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala aeno Nabiwi Godoko baęž‰gala aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰suku ibaęž‰te gabo naęž‰hiduimaęž‰menaęž‰ ale laęž‰tamo kopelamemaęž‰.  
\v 12 Baęž‰gala wadiyala Kodawate laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo ebeno malemale emalagidolo komo konomomaęž‰ naęž‰midaęž‰mene, baęž‰bene laęž‰ ipuwalo etapaęž‰te etapi malemalelo ba emalagidole laęž‰le komo hopo tawakalubi hiliyonomo atumu konomamo bemalagidolenamata, ale laęž‰ keba kaęž‰na kemalagidoletana baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.  
\v 13 Baęž‰gala wadiyala aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰suti baęž‰moe gabodo laęž‰eno tepo ipuwa naęž‰kodakoduilamaęž‰mene, baęž‰bene ebete ebeno talona taęž‰matapi hiliyonomago gala daęž‰kapemene, baęž‰ba tetelo laęž‰le aeno Nabiwi Godokono holoholo hapulu tuputupupinomomaęž‰ ba edaęž‰ha baęž‰bo konelaęž‰motaęž‰hanamaęž‰nemata, mabu laęž‰ ipuwalo eta kapiya kubate aęž‰kitanamene.   
\c 4  
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Ibino Emede Ipuwalo Godoko Keba Kaęž‰na Naęž‰kaęž‰kalakaluiminamenaęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ dopamo agodone iyaęž‰tawahuimata laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo laęž‰ Godoko keba kaęž‰na naęž‰kaęž‰kalakaluimionama, baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno kalakala bitana mabu laęž‰ baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na bemedenamata. Baęž‰bene baęž‰moe leta kuititi hapulu ale baęž‰moe komomaęž‰ laęž‰ Kodawa Yaęž‰sukunu mahilamo gala konomamo naęž‰kakiyalamaęž‰ta, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰be tuputupu emede ipuwalo ba polaęž‰na laęž‰eno hidohido ododili ipuwalo napepehonalaęž‰,  
\v 2 iyo, ale dopamo Yaęž‰sugodone uwatete laęž‰tamo dikalami baęž‰bi tutumu tabo komokomo laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala.  
\v 3 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ Godokono ubi baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰nala, laęž‰le ebeno talona emede ipuwalo ba polaęž‰na bohele pilo komo baęž‰gala eta dubuino kamena pilo komo baęž‰makomako kuba komokomo akododilaęž‰laęž‰.  
\v 4 Wadiyala laęž‰ hiliyonomate huiyatiya hidohido baęž‰gala talona emede ukui kapiya nuwatiyaęž‰laęž‰, hiliyonomo tetelo laęž‰eno kateneno kuba ubi komate laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno hido mulu ukui komamo hibilo kopapamilaęž‰halenamaęž‰.  
\v 5 Numaęž‰laęž‰, puyaęž‰te ibino kateneno hilopo komokomo helonomamo daęž‰taęž‰matalena baęž‰bi kuba ododilipaęž‰te Godokono komo iyaęž‰tawahahaęž‰, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ebe ubihinola laęž‰le ibi huiyamaęž‰ edaęž‰ha.  
\v 6 Iyo, laęž‰le hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kapiya badininipalamaęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana, modobohaęž‰ etate ebeno lumagitamo kateneno kuba hilopo komo ododi, baęž‰gala modobohaęž‰ etate haęž‰da amiho gabodo ebeno ekawino eta hido komo pilolo lawe.  
\p Baęž‰ hibila, ale dopamo laęž‰ konomamo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na aęž‰kiyahalamiaęž‰ta, puyaęž‰te baęž‰mako kuba komokomo dododilina Godote ibaęž‰tamo huiya hibilo kikalamemaęž‰ne.  
\v 7 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote a hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te ebeno talona emede ipuwalo kopolaęž‰namaęž‰ a yaęž‰lo aęž‰kaęž‰miyaęž‰, iyo, ebe ubihinola ale kateneno kubakuba ubi komoeno ododili ipuwalo kemedenamaęž‰.  
\v 8 Baęž‰gala eta komo. Godote ebeno Gobogobo laęž‰tamo nikalamenata laęž‰le ebeno talonapimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ ipuwalo etate aeno iyaęž‰tulame tabo ubihaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰na, ebete hopo lumagino tutumu tabomaęž‰ ebeno ubihaęž‰ komo kahawakaliminahaęž‰, ao, ebeno ododi ipuwalo ebete Godokono tutumu tabomaęž‰ ebeno ubihaęž‰ komo behawakalimina.   
\p
\v 9-10 Baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰moe eta komo naęž‰kumaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰le hibimaęž‰ midipi malemalelo kemalagidolenamaęž‰ Godote laęž‰ dopamo iyaęž‰tulamiaęž‰ta. Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰le ebeno tabamo papamilaęž‰halelo Maęž‰sadoniya hoponapi hibimaęž‰ midipi ekaki hiliyonomo naęž‰malemalelatelenakomata, huiyatiya aeno ekakaęž‰laęž‰, kubahaęž‰ ale baęž‰moe leta ipuwalo Godokono malemale emalagidolo komomaęž‰ laęž‰ gala kakakiyalamemaęž‰, iyo, a ubi konomola baęž‰moe eta kapiya tabo laęž‰ kokiyalamemaęž‰naęž‰ta, wadiyala laęž‰ Godokono malemale ipuwalo gala naęž‰kapepehalaęž‰.  
\v 11 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ laęž‰eno ubi konomamo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na nihatenalaęž‰, laęž‰le komo tawakalubaęž‰go tatabalo ba emedena komopino komomaęž‰ tabo gaęž‰laheno laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰eno emede komokomo kapiya hidamo kulamemaęž‰nemata. Baęž‰gala kebe modobohaęž‰ komokomo laęž‰godolo daęž‰polaęž‰na, hegehege mani oko owatiho ipuwalo laęž‰ haęž‰kiya baęž‰bi komo naęž‰modobuilamenakuyaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰ dopamo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰kiyalamiti baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.  
\v 12 Numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰moe komamo hibilo daęž‰papamilaęž‰halema, baęž‰ba tetelo laęž‰ mani baęž‰gala ilina tawakalubaęž‰godone dito uwatemaęž‰ temeteme ibaęž‰tamo aęž‰kikalamaęž‰mata, iyo, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te laęž‰eno tuputupu ododili komo dulamelelamemenaęž‰ ibaęž‰te laęž‰ hidohido tawakalubimaęž‰ baęž‰bo kogaęž‰lamaęž‰naęž‰.   
\s1 Kodawa Yaęž‰sukunu Pe Komo  
\p
\v 13 Aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo daęž‰haęž‰lahui, a ubila laęž‰ ibino hibi komo hidamo niyaęž‰tawahalaęž‰, laęž‰le ibino haęž‰laha komomaęž‰ tepo ipuwalo menemene lawekapomaęž‰. Numaęž‰laęž‰, hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te ibino tawakalubino haęž‰laha komomaęž‰ kubanomamo ihiminaka, mabu ibaęž‰te Yaęž‰sukunu kalakala komo baęž‰gala ebeno pe komomaęž‰ uliholo kalatiminahaęž‰. Huiyatiya laęž‰ ibi huiyamaęž‰ akedaęž‰halaęž‰,  
\v 14 mabu a hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te iyaęž‰tawahala, Yaęž‰suti daęž‰hoiyaęž‰ ebete kaęž‰kaęž‰mo gala aęž‰kamahiguyaęž‰, iyo, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo daęž‰haęž‰lahamenaęž‰ Godote ibaęž‰tamo kaęž‰kaęž‰ gala kakikalamemaęž‰ne, ebete Yaęž‰sutamo kaęž‰kaęž‰ keba kaęž‰na kikamiyaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na, baęž‰bemaęž‰ kalakala konomola, ebeno pe hegelalo ebete ibi atamo gala kakamagahelemaęž‰ne!   
\p
\v 15 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kaęž‰lo ale laęž‰ diyaęž‰tulamita, baęž‰moe tabo baęž‰ Kodawoeno iyaęž‰tulame tabola. Baęž‰ hibila, Yaęž‰sukunu pe hegelalo a puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kaęž‰kaęž‰lo demedehonamaęž‰, Hunu Habamo konalehawaminamaęž‰ puyaęž‰te dopamo daęž‰haęž‰lahui ale baęž‰bi hibimaęž‰ midipi aęž‰kadopalamaęž‰maęž‰.  
\v 16 Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰be hegelalo Godote ebeno tabo madodo hunamo adipatelo modobo tabo daęž‰goewatamene, baęž‰ba tetelo hopo habanapaęž‰te Godokono gebole diyamo baęž‰gala ebeno helonomo nopodawoeno tabo madodo ulihote Kodawa Yaęž‰suti Hunu Habane baęž‰bo kopihitigamaęž‰ne. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo daęž‰haęž‰lahui, baęž‰baęž‰te dopamo kaęž‰kaęž‰mo mahilaęž‰halete,  
\v 17 baęž‰bene a puyaęž‰te hopo habalo demedehonamaęž‰ Yaęž‰suti a uwatete, a hibimaęž‰ midipi hiliyonomate ebaęž‰go alomo hunulu baęž‰bo konekapiyamaęž‰nemaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰ba tetene tupuimiti ale Kodawa Yaęž‰sukubaęž‰ emedena emedena tetelo bemedehonamaęž‰,  
\v 18 baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ ipuwalo baęž‰moe tabo komomaęž‰ etapaęž‰te etapi hidamo nowalubihuinakuyaęž‰laęž‰.   
\c 5  
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Yaęž‰sukunu Pe Komomaęž‰ Uliholo Naęž‰latiminamenaęž‰  
\p
\v 1-2 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, Kodawa Yaęž‰sukunu Ko Hegelalo kebe hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ komate dikulihomenaęž‰ baęž‰bi komomaęž‰ nale baęž‰moe leta ipuwalo laęž‰ koamo aęž‰kakiyalamaęž‰mata, mabu laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahanomola pilo dubuti du ipuwalo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰penako Yaęž‰suti baęž‰be Hegelalo baęž‰ba kaęž‰na kopemaęž‰ne.  
\v 3 Iyo, baęž‰be hegelate peheno dopamo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te baęž‰ma kaęž‰na baęž‰gaęž‰lanakomenaęž‰, â€śAeno emede komo baęž‰ hidonomola, baęž‰gala tole komote agodolo kitanahaęž‰ mabu hopo habanapaęž‰te hete ipuwalo bemedena.â€ť Huiyatiya baęž‰ba tetenomolo Godokono konomo olalatiti ibaęž‰tamo dito kuluhukumaęž‰ne, lamitu kamenate hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ komo ba ododili ebeno gudu alahimi temetemete ebetamo keba kaęž‰na kuluhukunako baęž‰ba kaęž‰na. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰ba tetelo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰tamo duluhukumini, ibaęž‰te baęž‰be olalati temeteme ipuwane alahutihomaęž‰ gabo nipo kohowadimaęž‰naęž‰!   
\p
\v 4 O hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, puyaęž‰te du konomolo u daęž‰lahanaka baęž‰baęž‰te pilo dubuino pe komo aęž‰kiyaęž‰tawahalaęž‰, huiyatiya laęž‰eno komo eba kaęž‰nahaęž‰! Laęž‰ du ipuwalo kemedenahaęž‰ huiyatiya laęž‰ Kodawoeno pe komomaęž‰ uliholo emedenamata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete ebeno Ko Hegelalo daęž‰pemene laęž‰le baęž‰be komo umiti aęž‰kalaęž‰waęž‰hamata.  
\v 5 Numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ hiliyonomate alo teteno gugudimaęž‰ edaęž‰hanamata, iyo, a hibimaęž‰ midipi du teteno gugudihaęž‰,  
\v 6-7 baęž‰bemaęž‰ komopaęž‰te u daęž‰lahanaka ale baęž‰bako tawakalubimaęž‰ edaęž‰ha modobohaęž‰, mabu du tete baęž‰ ibino u laha tetela baęž‰gala du tete baęž‰ ibino gamoda niho tetela. Wadiyala ale huiyatiya tuputupu ukuilo ba emedena aeno Kodawoeno pe komomaęž‰ uliholo kolatiminamaęž‰nemaęž‰,  
\v 8 iyo, a hibimaęž‰ midipi baęž‰ hegela teteno tawakalubila, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala ale hiliyonomo tetelo tuputupu ukuilo bemedenamaęž‰. Baęž‰gala wadiyala ale Godoko hibimaęž‰ midi komo baęž‰gala malemale emalagidolo komo, baęž‰bi netewa koko komo aeno apaęž‰mo kopupulimaęž‰nemaęž‰, alaholodawate ebeno nehe ilina daęž‰pulinako baęž‰ba kaęž‰na. Baęž‰gala ale aeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo Yaęž‰sugodone hibilo lawemaęž‰, wadiyala ale ebeno pe komomaęž‰ uliholo baęž‰latiminamaęž‰, mabu baęž‰bako uliho komo baęž‰ alaholodawoeno diba huiyala.   
\p
\v 9 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote a kakaęž‰miyaęž‰haęž‰ ebete aeno kuba ododili mabumaęž‰ ebeno konomo mauba ipuwalo huiya atamo kikaaęž‰memaęž‰. Ao, ebete huiyatiya a uwatiyaęž‰ ale aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono oko komodo aeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo kolawemaęž‰,  
\v 10 mabu Yaęž‰sukunu hoe komoeno ipuwa baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰nala, ebe ubila ale emedena emedena tetelo ebaęž‰go kemedenamaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kalakala konomola, hibimaęž‰ midipi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te dopamo daęž‰haęž‰lahui baęž‰gala puyaęž‰te ebeno pe hegelalo hopo habalo demedehonamenaęž‰, ibi hiliyonomate kapiya tetelo ibino hibi kalakala ebegodone konelawemaęž‰naęž‰.  
\v 11 Iyo, baęž‰moe mabumaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno tabo komamo baęž‰gala laęž‰eno ododili komamo laęž‰ ipuwalo etapaęž‰te etapi hidamo nowalubihuinakuyaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰ma tetelo keba kaęž‰na kododionama baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.   
\s1 Polote Leta Kuititi Hapulu Komo Iyaęž‰tulame Tabo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 12 Aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰ begoelamaęž‰ta laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te Kelisokono hibi gabo baęž‰gala emede komo laęž‰ iyaęž‰tulamemaęž‰ oko dowatina, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno ukuilo ibi hunamo wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelelo ibino tabamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanalaęž‰.  
\v 13 Numaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te laęž‰ kowalubilimaęž‰ hido oko bowatina, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ ibino tabamo hidonomamo ba papamilaęž‰hale ibi malemalelo nemalagidolenalaęž‰. Baęž‰gala eta komo, wadiyala laęž‰eno kapiyuimi ipuwalo laęž‰ hiliyonomate tatabalo nemedenalaęž‰.   
\p
\v 14 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, ale laęž‰ koamo naęž‰gaęž‰lalamaęž‰ta laęž‰ ipuwalo puyaęž‰te buhamamaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, wadiyala laęž‰le ibi naęž‰kiyahalamaęž‰laęž‰ oko hibilo kowatihomaęž‰. Baęž‰gala puyaęž‰te ibino hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo hilopo diyaęž‰tawahana baęž‰gala puyaęž‰te helohaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, wadiyala laęž‰le laęž‰eno tabamo baęž‰gala ododili komamo ibi nowalubiliyaęž‰laęž‰, iyo, laęž‰le komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hiliyonomo tawakalubi laęž‰eno tabamo dowalubilinakoma laęž‰le ibaęž‰tamo tiyolo ubihaęž‰maęž‰ akedaęž‰hanakalaęž‰.  
\v 15 Baęž‰gala baęž‰moe baęž‰ eta komola. Laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo etate etatamo kuba dododimini, baęž‰ba tetelo temeteme lawedawate kuba ododidawatamo huiya akikamaęž‰laęž‰, huiyatiya wadiyala laęž‰le hiliyonomo tetelo laęž‰eno ubi konomamo nihatenakuyaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ ipuwalo etate etatamo malemale ba hawakalimi komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tawakalubi hiliyonomatamo atumu hido komokomo kapiya kakododilinamaęž‰.   
\p
\v 16 Baęž‰bene hiliyonomo tetelo laęž‰le Godokono kalakalago ba emedena,  
\v 17 du baęž‰gala hegela hiliyonomolo ebaęž‰go tabo gaęž‰la komo ekelalameheno,  
\v 18 hidohido komate ikuliho tetelo baęž‰gala olalati komate ikuliho tetelo ebetamo kalakala tabo naęž‰wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelenakuyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰moi netewa-kapiya komo baęž‰ Godote laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo ulamemaęž‰ ubi dihatena baęž‰bi komola, mabu laęž‰le Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwalo ba emedena baęž‰bi hidohido komate laęž‰godolo nikulihonakamenaęž‰.   
\p
\v 19 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godokono Talona Gobogobote kebe oko kowatina baęž‰be oko akaduhimaęž‰laęž‰,  
\v 20 iyo, keba tetelo eta lumagiti Godokono ukui hibinomolo daęž‰hawakalimimini, wadiyala laęž‰le baęž‰be tabo lawete kubamaęž‰ akagaęž‰lalaęž‰.  
\v 21 Huiyatiya laęž‰ hidamo, tawakalubaęž‰te kebe hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tabo komo Godokono mahilamo dolamagiminaka, laęž‰le baęž‰bi hiliyonomo tabo komo laęž‰eno hido ukuiaęž‰mo anagilamete hibi tabonomomaęž‰ tiyolo akagaęž‰lalaęž‰. Baęž‰ baęž‰moe gabodo laęž‰le Godokono hibi tabo komokomo kodakodalo ba watilaęž‰motaęž‰na,  
\v 22 hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba tabo baęž‰gala ododili komokomo hiliyonomo laęž‰le gala hapuamo naęž‰midaliyaęž‰laęž‰.   
\p
\v 23 Baęž‰ hibila, kebe dawate a hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo hete dikaaęž‰mena, baęž‰be Kodawa baęž‰ Godotela, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ ebe baęž‰ma kaęž‰na toemehonakomaęž‰, ebete laęž‰eno emede komokomo hiliyonomo ipuwalo laęž‰ ebeno hibi talonapimaęž‰ ba midili, ebete laęž‰eno gobogoboeno ukui baęž‰gala tepo ipuwoeno ubi komo baęž‰gala ape konomoeno ododili komo hidamo nulamelelamenakamenaęž‰ta. Kalakala konomola, baęž‰ baęž‰moe gabodo Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono pe tetelo eta kuba dehaęž‰potonomote laęž‰ ipuwalo aęž‰kitanamene.  
\v 24 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote laęž‰ ebeno talonapimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hamaęž‰ kaęž‰laminata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebe modobola ebete baęž‰be hido oko laęž‰ ipuwalo upulaęž‰, iyo, ebete kebe komo ododilimaęž‰ tabo dolamagina ebete baęž‰bi komokomo hibinomolo bododilinakomene.   
\p
\v 25 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰ atumu a mabumaęž‰ Godotamo naęž‰toetoehonakuyaęž‰laęž‰,  
\v 26 baęž‰gala laęž‰ daęž‰kapiyuiminakoma, wadiyala laęž‰ hiliyonomo etapaęž‰te etapino kokoto uwatehuilo naęž‰paęž‰watamehuinakuyaęž‰laęž‰.  
\v 27 Na Polote Godokono mahilamo laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na goelamemata, laęž‰ baęž‰moe leta hibimaęž‰ midipi ekaki hiliyonomatamo naęž‰kaęž‰lamiholiyaęž‰laęž‰.   
\p
\v 28 Wadiyala aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono malemale komote laęž‰godolo nitanamene. Baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baęž‰baęž‰la. \fig Laęž‰le Godokobaęž‰ tabo gaęž‰la komo akekelalamaęž‰laęž‰|alt="Group praying on knees" src="CN02076B.tif" size="span" loc="1/2 of page" copy="1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="5.17" \fig*   